Package com.jfilegoodies.explorer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileExplorer
    A FileExplorer represents the GUI file-explorer provided by the OS.
    FileExplorers
    Provides factory/utility methods for FileExplorer objects.
    FileExplorers.LazyExplorer
    An LazyExplorer is a FileExplorer that wraps another FileExplorer object.
    LinuxFileExplorer
    A LinuxFileExplorer is a FileExplorer implementation that works on a Linux operating system.
    MacFileExplorer
    A MacFileExplorer is a FileExplorer implementation that works on a MacOS operating system.
    WindowsFileExplorer
    A WindowsFileExplorer is a FileExplorer implementation that works on a Microsoft Windows operating system.
